{"tid":2512982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嚇死！金正恩下令「看韓劇關15年」　北韓1萬學生火速自首換減刑","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T07:50:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc41db4be7bcef3fa62c7ee5b9ee7f48c8642ba9","tid":2512982,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"人氣韓劇《愛的迫降》中曾演出北韓民眾透過私下管道，非法觀賞南韓電視劇的場面，而該場面不但是現實生活中實際發生的事，近日，北韓政府為了阻擋南韓的文化入侵，更是宣布偷看南韓戲劇、電影者最高可處15年有期徒刑，隨後便傳出有超過1萬的北韓學生自首以求減刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5600/d5600896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5600%2Fd5600896.jpg&h=b34b1f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《愛的迫降》曾演出北韓民眾偷看韓劇片段 。（圖／翻攝tvN）<br />\n<br />\n北韓在去年12月底制定《反動思想文化排斥法》，民眾如果收看、傳播南韓電視劇，不只會被判處數年勞改，甚至可以判到死刑。根據韓媒《國民日報》報導，一位熟悉北韓當地情況的人士透露在該法開始實行後，2020年底在某都市裡共有超過1萬名的學生集體自首觀看了所謂的「不法影像」，並且上繳了5000多台的DVD播放器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5598/d5598581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5598%2Fd5598581.jpg&h=7ceeefaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲北韓領導人金正恩。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n隨後，當地政府把該消息通知到各市的朝鮮勞動黨委員會，想藉此鼓勵民眾舉報，官方認為單憑管制處罰，很難根除蔓延在全社會的韓流，而對於有高達1萬名的學生自首的消息，有專家表示「如果一個城市就有1萬名，那韓流已經廣泛傳播，不自首的人比自首的人更多」，而金正恩近日也下達指示，強調要「加強對北韓青年的思想控制和穿著的管制」。"},{"pid":"17ee8e9b3b48b2f29fb90de59be223f8b959ba00","tid":2512982,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"關彩..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee86556ed5d4e27ca83fa316f58c4a90bb40f11c","tid":2512982,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"我願意將樓豬條命獻俾肥仔恩代替呢班無辜北韓人受罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47435fcad9b73f74b7fb329a6652f44fcaffd30e","tid":2512982,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"咁轉睇日劇咪得"},{"pid":"43c610b1e74b3af60cfa6031211f2299dee8fc73","tid":2512982,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"irene都收服不了金仔的心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc61e741913eb1080f16e5a55f984158b87fa0f2","tid":2512982,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47435fcad9b73f74b7fb329a6652f44fcaffd30e","tid":2512982,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"咁轉睇日劇咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地好似要拎VCD睇"},{"pid":"224f6ccd8bf9b00b52cadbf32a0ad5932349cdfb","tid":2512982,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"自己睇IRENE就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06333380ed2206e9553e1d22eaff4ab09bbbf57d","tid":2512982,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:50:10.000Z","msg":"自己睇NBA就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823d9f42a5b25eecef3be4f7f9e67c053d44c72c","tid":2512982,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"主席屌女就得，人民睇片打飛機都冇權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTV0iET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTV0iET.jpg&h=99345f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}